WEBVTT

01:38.229 --> 01:40.759
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.240 --> 01:43.590
[Episode 20]

01:59.110 --> 02:03.040
♪ Honor and disgrace;
rumors and prejudice ♪

02:03.830 --> 02:07.240
♪ Everyone has their own take ♪

02:07.870 --> 02:11.700
♪ Fingers coated in blood
and disasters brought about ♪

02:10.590 --> 02:11.720
If you're not going to make a move,

02:11.720 --> 02:14.950
♪ Were never what I wanted ♪

02:13.000 --> 02:14.000
I'm leaving.

02:15.250 --> 02:19.090
♪ The great way is fading away,
besieged by mysterious traps ♪

02:19.950 --> 02:23.710
♪ Who dares to treat life and death
as nothing? ♪

02:23.730 --> 02:27.450
♪ In the blink of an eye, the body
collapses, and the soul is destroyed ♪

02:27.480 --> 02:32.450
♪ The fire starts raging across the land ♪

02:33.230 --> 02:35.270
♪ What do you think is ♪

02:35.290 --> 02:37.570
♪ The most impressive farewell
in the world? ♪

02:37.940 --> 02:41.070
♪ The endless slaughter and massacres ♪

02:41.910 --> 02:45.870
♪ Do not wait until that thin snow
on the eaves ♪

02:45.890 --> 02:49.120
♪ Turns a young man's hair white
before you regret it ♪

02:49.670 --> 02:51.410
♪ When do you think ♪

02:51.430 --> 02:53.870
♪ The bloody strife will come to an end? ♪

02:53.890 --> 02:57.210
♪ Burn myself to prove it
without looking back ♪

02:57.760 --> 03:01.740
♪ Holding the morning glow in hand,
I paint the world ♪

03:01.770 --> 03:07.950
♪ The dawn light
illuminates the vast sky ♪

03:15.180 --> 03:19.190
♪ Honor and disgrace;
rumors and prejudice ♪

03:19.940 --> 03:22.940
♪ Everyone has their own take ♪

03:23.850 --> 03:27.490
♪ Fingers coated in blood
and disasters brought about ♪

03:27.720 --> 03:30.890
♪ Were never what I wanted ♪

03:31.220 --> 03:34.960
♪ The great way is fading away,
besieged by mysterious traps ♪

03:35.850 --> 03:39.630
♪ Who dares to treat life and death
as nothing? ♪

03:39.650 --> 03:43.579
♪ In the blink of an eye, the body
collapses, and the soul is destroyed ♪

03:43.610 --> 03:47.070
♪ The fire starts raging across the land ♪

03:47.190 --> 03:49.210
♪ What do you think is ♪

03:49.230 --> 03:51.570
♪ The most impressive farewell
in the world? ♪

03:51.840 --> 03:55.150
♪ The endless slaughter and massacres ♪

03:55.880 --> 03:59.750
♪ Do not wait until that thin snow
on the eaves ♪

04:00.150 --> 04:03.120
♪ Turns a young man's hair white
before you regret it ♪

04:03.630 --> 04:05.220
♪ When do you think ♪

04:05.240 --> 04:07.670
♪ The bloody strife will come to an end? ♪

04:07.940 --> 04:10.920
♪ End these everlasting battles ♪

04:11.800 --> 04:15.730
♪ Holding the morning glow in hand,
I paint the world ♪

04:15.860 --> 04:20.149
♪ Someone's got to clean up this mess ♪

05:06.630 --> 05:08.270
Don't come any closer.

05:14.950 --> 05:15.560
Senior!

05:16.830 --> 05:17.460
Senior!

05:19.950 --> 05:21.210
Senior, where are you?

05:22.040 --> 05:22.600
Sheng.

05:24.870 --> 05:25.430
Senior.

05:26.310 --> 05:26.870
Sheng!

05:27.160 --> 05:27.830
Senior!

05:33.600 --> 05:34.240
Senior.

05:36.040 --> 05:36.800
Senior!

05:56.310 --> 05:56.830
No!

05:56.950 --> 05:57.310
No!

05:57.430 --> 05:57.830
No...

06:00.070 --> 06:00.920
Don't come any closer.

06:00.920 --> 06:01.800
Don't come any closer!

06:01.800 --> 06:03.060
Don't come any closer!

06:06.240 --> 06:06.870
No!

06:07.430 --> 06:08.630
Don't come any closer.

06:08.630 --> 06:10.270
Don't come any closer...

06:10.720 --> 06:11.980
Don't come any closer!

06:23.190 --> 06:24.240
Everyone in the back, keep up.

06:24.240 --> 06:24.800
Hurry up!

06:26.310 --> 06:26.800
Coming.

06:36.870 --> 06:37.510
Senior.

06:39.180 --> 06:39.840
This is bad.

06:39.860 --> 06:41.920
The Young Sect Master has been taken!

06:45.260 --> 06:46.060
Senior Jiang,

06:46.159 --> 06:48.090
please save the Young Sect Master.

06:48.240 --> 06:48.970
Who took him?

06:49.659 --> 06:50.950
Someone from Chongling Valley.

06:50.950 --> 06:52.480
He claimed to be Su Taiyi's Master.

06:52.480 --> 06:53.560
He looked quite young.

06:53.560 --> 06:54.630
We couldn't tell his actual age.

06:54.630 --> 06:55.560
Su Taiyi's master.

06:55.560 --> 06:56.600
is just a physician.

06:56.600 --> 06:57.720
What kind of cultivation could he have?

06:57.720 --> 06:58.360
Lin Muhan

06:58.830 --> 06:59.310
is a cultivator

06:59.310 --> 07:00.800
at the peak of Foundation Establishment.

07:00.800 --> 07:01.360
His father also

07:01.360 --> 07:03.160
equipped him with magical artifacts.

07:03.160 --> 07:05.430
Even someone at the Golden Core Stage
is no challenge for him.

07:05.430 --> 07:06.760
How did he get captured?

07:06.950 --> 07:08.310
His power is unfathomable.

07:08.310 --> 07:09.510
At Chongling Valley,

07:09.620 --> 07:10.800
he struck Mr. Bai Yun down

07:10.800 --> 07:11.680
with a single palm,

07:11.680 --> 07:13.080
and injured Cang Fengzi.

07:13.330 --> 07:14.940
Bai Zongying from Tianyuan Sect

07:14.940 --> 07:17.000
stood by and didn't dare make a sound.

07:17.210 --> 07:18.510
With the Young Sect Master's skills,

07:18.510 --> 07:20.370
it's normal that he was captured.

07:20.730 --> 07:21.660
How did Lin Muhan

07:22.330 --> 07:24.000
provoke this formidable enemy?

07:24.000 --> 07:25.430
He didn't exactly provoke him.

07:25.430 --> 07:26.340
Actually,

07:27.130 --> 07:28.390
they are somewhat friends.

07:28.390 --> 07:29.830
The situation was too chaotic that day.

07:29.830 --> 07:31.070
We were fighting the demonic cultivators

07:31.070 --> 07:32.100
from the Wushuang Society,

07:32.100 --> 07:33.159
and he was fighting

07:33.159 --> 07:33.920
the people from Qinghong Sect.

07:33.920 --> 07:35.120
Later, he was losing,

07:35.280 --> 07:36.560
and the Young Sect Master
couldn't bear to watch it,

07:36.560 --> 07:37.950
so he helped him out a bit.

07:37.950 --> 07:38.830
He helped him,

07:39.440 --> 07:40.770
but still got captured?

07:41.159 --> 07:41.750
Yes.

07:42.310 --> 07:43.240
And then,

07:43.270 --> 07:45.240
the big guy from Qinghong Sect died,

07:45.240 --> 07:46.270
and the rest fled.

07:46.680 --> 07:47.630
As the Young Sect Master

07:47.630 --> 07:49.190
was capturing those demonic cultivators,

07:49.190 --> 07:50.920
he was suddenly grabbed and taken away.

07:50.920 --> 07:51.600
Before leaving,

07:51.600 --> 07:52.630
he left a message.

07:53.510 --> 07:54.310
What message?

07:54.510 --> 07:55.630
"If any of you dare make a move,

07:55.630 --> 07:57.630
I will kill your Young Sect Master."

08:02.260 --> 08:03.000
He is protecting

08:03.000 --> 08:04.660
Wushuang Society's members.

08:04.870 --> 08:06.190
How did Chongling Valley
and Wushuang Society

08:06.190 --> 08:07.650
end up helping each other?

08:07.920 --> 08:09.050
I don't know about that either.

08:09.050 --> 08:10.480
But isn't it normal

08:10.510 --> 08:11.070
for members of Chongling Valley
and Wushuang Society

08:11.070 --> 08:12.130
to help each other?

08:12.430 --> 08:13.120
Just look at

08:13.390 --> 08:15.100
his attitude towards ordinary mortals

08:15.100 --> 08:16.090
and his attitude

08:16.120 --> 08:17.920
towards us in the immortal sect.

08:20.140 --> 08:20.970
Senior Jiang,

08:21.000 --> 08:22.210
what should we do now?

08:22.560 --> 08:23.490
What do you mean?

08:23.510 --> 08:25.020
The Young Sect Master has been captured.

08:25.020 --> 08:25.750
We must save him.

08:25.750 --> 08:27.120
Isn't that your business?

08:27.120 --> 08:28.040
Mine?

08:28.480 --> 08:30.070
I came here on my master's orders

08:30.070 --> 08:32.380
to capture the people of Wushuang Society.

08:32.380 --> 08:34.059
I don't care about anything else.

08:34.059 --> 08:35.150
Nangong Guhong and I

08:35.150 --> 08:36.409
will continue forward

08:36.669 --> 08:37.600
to Phoenix City.

08:38.030 --> 08:39.120
That is the ultimate goal

08:39.120 --> 08:40.320
of Wushuang Society.

08:42.240 --> 08:43.570
Take your people and go.

08:43.960 --> 08:45.160
Go and save Lin Muhan.

08:51.440 --> 08:52.170
Who's there?

09:00.870 --> 09:01.510
Don't run!

09:30.750 --> 09:31.320
Xin.

09:32.240 --> 09:33.150
They ate my leg.

09:33.270 --> 09:34.240
They ate my leg!

09:34.600 --> 09:35.120
Kill me!

09:35.220 --> 09:36.720
Quick, kill me!

09:38.630 --> 09:39.270
Yes.

09:39.960 --> 09:40.760
The War Demons

09:41.270 --> 09:42.080
are all evil.

09:42.910 --> 09:44.500
You're a disciple of the immortal sect.

09:44.500 --> 09:46.150
I am a remnant of the War Demons.

09:46.150 --> 09:47.150
It's only natural

09:47.550 --> 09:48.880
that you want to kill me.

09:57.550 --> 09:58.350
Go find Sheng.

09:58.720 --> 10:00.080
Tell her not to take risks

10:00.080 --> 10:00.880
and come back as soon as possible.

10:00.880 --> 10:02.550
Don't take risks,
come back as soon as possible.

10:02.550 --> 10:03.120
Tell her,

10:03.670 --> 10:04.930
I am worried about her.

10:05.240 --> 10:06.300
Worried about her.

10:06.390 --> 10:07.450
Worried about her.

10:30.560 --> 10:35.270
[Phoenix City]

10:53.030 --> 10:53.840
Come, Lu.

10:54.420 --> 10:55.350
It's time to eat.

10:57.390 --> 10:58.030
Lu.

11:01.910 --> 11:02.550
Lu?

11:04.900 --> 11:05.550
Have your injuries

11:05.550 --> 11:06.630
worsened again?

11:07.960 --> 11:08.510
Right,

11:09.150 --> 11:09.670
I have

11:10.120 --> 11:11.720
the last two Yangyuan Pills here.

11:11.720 --> 11:12.250
Eat them.

11:12.630 --> 11:13.750
You'll have strength after that.

11:13.750 --> 11:14.390
No need.

11:15.620 --> 11:16.820
What day is it today?

11:16.910 --> 11:17.510
Today?

11:17.820 --> 11:18.750
July 15th.

11:19.320 --> 11:19.960
Oh yeah,

11:20.320 --> 11:21.720
it's the Ghost Festival.

11:23.120 --> 11:23.630
Later,

11:24.150 --> 11:25.300
leave the city from the west gate

11:25.300 --> 11:26.510
and keep walking south.

11:26.510 --> 11:28.370
You'll reach the inn we came from.

11:29.670 --> 11:30.720
Are we going back?

11:31.200 --> 11:32.930
You are going back by yourself.

11:33.910 --> 11:35.390
You brought me here,

11:35.410 --> 11:36.940
and now you want me to leave?

11:37.360 --> 11:38.290
I'm not leaving.

11:42.760 --> 11:44.820
Here comes the sheep blood tofu stew.

11:45.030 --> 11:45.670
Let's eat.

11:46.940 --> 11:48.540
Enjoy your meal, gentlemen.

11:48.670 --> 11:49.200
Lu,

11:49.670 --> 11:50.980
you must try this.

11:51.440 --> 11:52.720
The sheep blood tofu stew

11:52.720 --> 11:54.250
is a North Xiang specialty.

11:54.400 --> 11:56.220
Phoenix City makes the
most authentic ones.

11:56.220 --> 11:57.750
They use fresh sheep blood.

11:58.000 --> 11:58.540
By the way,

11:58.540 --> 12:00.080
I took a peek in the backyard.

12:00.080 --> 12:01.740
They're using young lambs.

12:01.850 --> 12:02.680
Very tender.

12:07.910 --> 12:09.040
Why isn't it cooked?

12:09.790 --> 12:10.450
Attendant!

12:10.730 --> 12:12.670
The sheep blood isn't fully cooked!

12:12.670 --> 12:13.550
Come here and take a look.

12:13.550 --> 12:14.210
Attendant!

12:14.670 --> 12:15.330
Attendant!

12:22.390 --> 12:24.120
Hurry up and get me a cooked one.

12:24.150 --> 12:24.880
I am so sorry.

12:25.240 --> 12:26.270
I will get you a new one right away.

12:26.270 --> 12:27.530
I will get you a new one.

12:32.760 --> 12:33.590
Where is he?

12:45.220 --> 12:45.820
Qianqiao,

12:46.390 --> 12:48.120
your Bloodthirst is acting up.

12:48.670 --> 12:49.360
Mother...

12:50.250 --> 12:50.960
Go kill him.

12:51.480 --> 12:53.270
Then you won't feel so miserable.

12:53.270 --> 12:54.200
You killing them

12:54.270 --> 12:54.840
is like them

12:54.840 --> 12:56.020
slaughtering a chicken

12:56.020 --> 12:56.960
or a dog at will.

12:57.240 --> 12:58.170
Cats catch mice,

12:58.320 --> 12:59.310
and humans eat meat.

12:59.310 --> 13:00.570
It's the law of nature.

13:00.960 --> 13:01.680
And we

13:02.270 --> 13:03.790
were born to eat them.

13:04.840 --> 13:05.480
Do it.

13:06.340 --> 13:07.330
Drain their blood,

13:07.330 --> 13:08.390
and you'll be free.

13:13.630 --> 13:14.120
No.

13:15.720 --> 13:16.270
No!

13:16.410 --> 13:17.050
Do it.

13:17.870 --> 13:18.600
Do it!

13:19.240 --> 13:20.150
Do it!

15:04.630 --> 15:05.360
You again.

15:06.780 --> 15:07.630
I was just wondering

15:07.630 --> 15:09.430
where to find you for my revenge.

15:09.740 --> 15:11.670
And here you've found me yourself.

15:11.960 --> 15:12.510
Jiang Ji,

15:12.910 --> 15:14.510
aren't you going to stab her?

15:15.550 --> 15:16.410
After that day,

15:16.810 --> 15:18.610
I tossed and turned every night,

15:18.770 --> 15:20.630
worried that Senior Jin Lun
had struck too hard

15:20.630 --> 15:21.830
and finished you off,

15:21.840 --> 15:23.240
giving you a quick death.

15:23.480 --> 15:24.280
Fortunately,

15:25.080 --> 15:26.340
you didn't let me down.

15:26.630 --> 15:28.600
You think reaching the Golden Core Stage

15:28.600 --> 15:29.800
is enough to catch me?

15:30.630 --> 15:31.920
I'm not stopping there.

15:31.920 --> 15:33.320
Not only will I catch you,

15:33.810 --> 15:34.870
but I will also lock you up,

15:34.870 --> 15:36.130
torture you every day,

15:36.240 --> 15:38.240
and make you wish you were dead.

16:20.090 --> 16:20.940
It's you.

16:23.000 --> 16:23.860
Do you know her?

16:24.440 --> 16:25.910
She's a disciple of Xin Xie Manor.

16:25.910 --> 16:26.770
Sheng, I think.

16:27.340 --> 16:28.200
Before, in Chongling Valley,

16:28.200 --> 16:29.130
I met her senior,

16:29.230 --> 16:30.320
and almost got into a fight

16:30.320 --> 16:31.920
with Bai Zongying's people.

16:34.240 --> 16:35.390
This is my senior.

16:35.910 --> 16:38.360
She left the mountain for errands
and hasn't returned for a long time.

16:38.360 --> 16:39.270
You know her,

16:39.840 --> 16:40.440
don't you?

16:41.750 --> 16:43.210
What's her senior's name?

16:43.230 --> 16:43.780
Xin Mei.

16:52.390 --> 16:53.850
Still won't admit defeat?

16:54.030 --> 16:55.290
As long as I'm not dead,

16:55.390 --> 16:56.390
I have not lost.

16:58.440 --> 16:59.670
I see.

17:01.150 --> 17:03.080
I didn't expect a mere Xin Xie Manor

17:03.150 --> 17:04.069
to stir up

17:04.069 --> 17:05.400
such a huge wave.

18:00.880 --> 18:01.350
Stop.

18:01.640 --> 18:02.110
Stop.

18:04.870 --> 18:05.430
Madam Wu.

18:05.700 --> 18:06.830
There is a girl here.

18:13.060 --> 18:16.960
[Madam Wu]

18:13.900 --> 18:15.070
She looks decent

18:15.880 --> 18:17.080
and has a good figure.

18:18.550 --> 18:19.440
Let's take her back.

18:19.440 --> 18:20.000
Yes.

18:24.440 --> 18:25.000
Here.

18:25.350 --> 18:26.480
Boss, this way please.

18:26.480 --> 18:27.030
Here.

18:27.550 --> 18:29.070
The work this time isn't that heavy.

18:29.070 --> 18:29.830
Once it's done,

18:29.830 --> 18:31.090
we'll take a good rest.

18:31.200 --> 18:31.750
Sure.

18:33.160 --> 18:34.120
When we get into the city,

18:34.120 --> 18:35.400
we'll find a good restaurant

18:35.400 --> 18:36.750
and have a good drink.

18:37.070 --> 18:37.870
That's great.

18:38.400 --> 18:39.030
Here.

18:39.200 --> 18:39.680
Okay.

18:40.830 --> 18:41.960
I'll treat you then.

18:42.790 --> 18:43.680
Sure.

18:44.960 --> 18:46.090
When did you arrive?

18:46.720 --> 18:47.520
A few days ago.

18:49.510 --> 18:50.960
What took you guys so long?

18:50.960 --> 18:52.820
We got new information
right before we set off.

18:52.820 --> 18:54.260
Those demonic cultivators

18:54.260 --> 18:55.010
split into 3 groups

18:55.010 --> 18:56.590
while heading for Phoenix City.

18:56.590 --> 18:57.310
So we had no choice but to

18:57.310 --> 18:59.310
split into 3 groups to go after them.

19:00.440 --> 19:02.240
Senior Bai led the Tianyuan Sect,

19:02.240 --> 19:03.480
Jiang Ji and I moved together,

19:03.480 --> 19:04.880
and Lin Muhan went alone.

19:04.880 --> 19:06.080
Lin Muhan went alone?

19:07.270 --> 19:09.070
You were supposed to go with him,

19:09.080 --> 19:11.110
but your Master said
you had already hit the road.

19:11.110 --> 19:12.030
So we made a temporary arrangement

19:12.030 --> 19:13.090
for him to go alone.

19:13.160 --> 19:15.290
We don't expect him to succeed anyway.

19:15.400 --> 19:16.460
It doesn't matter.

19:17.000 --> 19:18.270
We have already succeeded

19:18.270 --> 19:20.460
and eliminated
all the demonic cultivators.

19:20.460 --> 19:21.460
Senior Bai's side

19:21.480 --> 19:23.070
probably won't have any problems either.

19:23.070 --> 19:25.160
Didn't they say
it was enough to capture them?

19:25.160 --> 19:26.350
You killed them all?

19:27.070 --> 19:28.880
Wushuang Society
is not to be trifled with.

19:28.880 --> 19:30.140
They had experts, too.

19:30.680 --> 19:31.540
Capturing them

19:31.680 --> 19:32.810
was not an easy task.

19:33.550 --> 19:34.310
What's more,

19:35.550 --> 19:37.400
they were all demonic cultivators.

19:37.400 --> 19:38.240
It's not a pity

19:39.310 --> 19:40.440
killing them at all.

19:42.510 --> 19:43.370
One more thing.

19:44.040 --> 19:46.100
The female cultivator in the capital

19:46.110 --> 19:46.880
is Xin Mei.

19:47.640 --> 19:48.510
How do you know?

19:49.000 --> 19:50.330
We met that woman again.

19:50.480 --> 19:51.110
Who?

19:51.640 --> 19:52.700
The one who stopped

19:52.720 --> 19:54.380
Nangong and me on our way here.

19:54.480 --> 19:56.000
She is also a disciple of Xin Xie Manor,

19:56.000 --> 19:56.780
named Sheng.

19:57.240 --> 19:58.890
The senior she was looking for before

19:58.890 --> 19:59.650
was Xin Mei.

20:00.290 --> 20:01.240
You fought her?

20:02.240 --> 20:02.960
Yes.

20:03.570 --> 20:04.330
How is she?

20:10.160 --> 20:10.960
I mean,

20:11.680 --> 20:12.790
she is quite skilled

20:12.790 --> 20:14.070
and has high cultivation.

20:14.070 --> 20:15.070
Are you guys okay?

20:15.480 --> 20:16.140
We are fine.

20:16.880 --> 20:18.400
Last time, she played some tricks.

20:18.400 --> 20:19.860
This time, we met head-on.

20:19.920 --> 20:21.960
Jiang Ji's cultivation has improved too.

20:21.960 --> 20:23.550
She had no chance to hurt her.

20:23.550 --> 20:25.400
I am already at the Golden Core Stage.

20:25.400 --> 20:26.530
So you captured her?

20:27.000 --> 20:28.200
Where did you put her?

20:30.000 --> 20:30.860
You killed her?

20:30.920 --> 20:31.510
Yes.

20:32.920 --> 20:34.650
Just as she was about to escape,

20:35.440 --> 20:37.900
Jiang Ji struck her
with her sword from afar.

20:38.200 --> 20:39.310
But we didn't find

20:39.400 --> 20:40.330
her body either.

20:40.680 --> 20:42.340
Your sword pierced her chest.

20:42.350 --> 20:43.720
In this vast desert,

20:44.200 --> 20:45.060
where could she

20:45.640 --> 20:46.770
possibly escape to?

20:47.920 --> 20:49.050
She won't live long.

21:31.640 --> 21:32.310
Sheng.

21:34.920 --> 21:35.470
Sheng!

21:38.110 --> 21:38.750
Sheng!

21:40.310 --> 21:40.960
Sheng.

21:41.650 --> 21:42.060
Sh...

21:43.780 --> 21:45.360
♪ I accept the blame of
numerous accusations ♪

21:45.380 --> 21:47.770
♪ I offer no defense ♪

21:47.790 --> 21:51.250
♪ To protect what I believe is worth it ♪

21:48.400 --> 21:49.550
Sheng. Sheng!

21:49.830 --> 21:50.400
Wake up.

21:50.750 --> 21:51.350
Sheng!

21:51.430 --> 21:53.300
♪ I admit my heart
is as hard as iron and stone ♪

21:53.330 --> 21:55.330
♪ Call me cold if you must ♪

21:55.350 --> 21:58.640
♪ I'll risk it all ♪

21:56.680 --> 21:58.030
Sheng. Sheng!

21:58.510 --> 21:59.040
Let's go.

22:04.910 --> 22:08.020
[Phoenix City]

22:23.380 --> 22:24.710
Are you feeling better?

22:24.790 --> 22:26.110
Why did you come to North Xiang?

22:26.110 --> 22:27.110
It's the Ghost Festival.

22:27.110 --> 22:28.260
I was afraid your Bloodthirst
would act up

22:28.260 --> 22:29.460
and put you in danger.

22:31.450 --> 22:32.310
What time is it?

22:33.720 --> 22:34.580
It's past 9 p.m.

22:35.000 --> 22:36.000
Your Bloodthirst

22:36.030 --> 22:36.760
flares up

22:36.790 --> 22:37.960
every year during the Ghost Festival.

22:37.960 --> 22:38.720
But this time,

22:38.720 --> 22:40.190
it's far worse than before.

22:40.190 --> 22:41.720
The more unstable your state of mind is,

22:41.720 --> 22:43.780
the harder it is to control yourself.

22:45.750 --> 22:46.270
Lu.

22:47.330 --> 22:48.860
You need to rest for a while.

22:49.110 --> 22:50.970
Don't fight with anyone anymore.

22:51.720 --> 22:52.580
Not yet.

22:53.160 --> 22:54.620
The young man after Xin Mei

22:54.770 --> 22:56.590
is a cultivator at the Void Stage.

22:56.590 --> 22:57.790
He is quite powerful.

22:58.420 --> 22:59.880
I can't figure out his background,

22:59.880 --> 23:01.410
which makes me feel uneasy.

23:01.590 --> 23:02.720
As for the Qinghong Sect,

23:02.720 --> 23:04.510
another of their Dharma Kings is dead.

23:04.510 --> 23:06.110
We have no idea

23:06.270 --> 23:07.870
who they will blame for this.

23:08.790 --> 23:10.310
I haven't been gone for long,

23:10.310 --> 23:11.710
yet so much has happened.

23:12.790 --> 23:13.440
Xin Mei

23:13.960 --> 23:15.560
found out about my identity.

23:17.830 --> 23:18.830
So you had a fight?

23:21.110 --> 23:21.750
You knew?

23:22.480 --> 23:23.210
I guessed it.

23:23.720 --> 23:25.180
While you were passed out,

23:25.400 --> 23:26.540
you kept mumbling something

23:26.540 --> 23:27.320
about Xin Mei

23:27.350 --> 23:28.210
and War Demons.

23:31.090 --> 23:32.120
Tell me about it.

23:32.310 --> 23:33.510
How did she treat you?

23:33.680 --> 23:34.680
Did she try to kill you?

23:34.680 --> 23:36.350
There's nothing to talk about.

23:36.350 --> 23:37.590
War Demons and the Human Race

23:37.590 --> 23:39.110
have a deep-seated hatred for each other.

23:39.110 --> 23:40.270
Anyone who found out my identity

23:40.270 --> 23:41.670
would react the same way.

23:42.160 --> 23:43.020
No matter what,

23:43.510 --> 23:45.030
these things started because of me,

23:45.030 --> 23:46.680
so the responsibility is mine.

23:46.680 --> 23:48.540
I can't just sit by and do nothing.

23:51.160 --> 23:52.620
I really should let her see

23:52.730 --> 23:54.730
how warm-hearted you are right now.

23:55.360 --> 23:56.200
You don't look like

23:56.200 --> 23:57.200
a War Demon at all.

24:00.200 --> 24:01.130
When do we leave?

24:02.510 --> 24:03.200
Tomorrow.

24:04.920 --> 24:06.160
Big bets, big payouts;

24:06.160 --> 24:07.690
small bets, small payouts.

24:07.880 --> 24:08.960
Roll the dice! Roll the dice!

24:08.960 --> 24:10.480
Place your bets! Hurry up!

24:12.880 --> 24:15.330
Big bets, big payouts;
small bets, small payouts.

24:15.330 --> 24:16.830
Big! Big! Big!

24:15.990 --> 24:17.810
[Sha Sanxing]

24:17.160 --> 24:18.400
All bets are final.

24:18.590 --> 24:20.000
Big! Big! Big!

24:20.200 --> 24:21.200
Big! Big! Big!

24:21.200 --> 24:22.200
Reveal.

24:22.510 --> 24:23.160
Small.

24:24.400 --> 24:25.240
Again, again!

24:25.510 --> 24:26.070
I lost again.

24:26.070 --> 24:27.000
You plan to look for Sha Sanxing,

24:27.000 --> 24:27.760
that lackey?

24:27.790 --> 24:28.650
Let me tell you,

24:28.680 --> 24:29.630
he has a bad character.

24:29.630 --> 24:31.480
Don't associate yourself with him.

24:31.480 --> 24:32.510
Another round.

24:32.810 --> 24:34.070
Keep betting. Come on.

24:34.250 --> 24:35.690
Come on, bet.

24:35.720 --> 24:36.350
Bet on big. Big!

24:36.350 --> 24:37.070
I'll bet on big.

24:37.070 --> 24:37.960
Big! Big! Big!

24:38.030 --> 24:39.360
Come on, bet on big. Big!

24:43.350 --> 24:44.480
Why are you running?

24:45.440 --> 24:46.600
For a moment,

24:46.790 --> 24:49.000
I didn't know why,

24:49.920 --> 24:51.780
but my legs wouldn't listen to me.

24:52.500 --> 24:53.370
I swear.

24:54.000 --> 24:54.830
After you left,

24:54.830 --> 24:57.070
I didn't commit any
arson, murder, or theft.

24:57.070 --> 24:58.750
I'm a law-abiding citizen now,

24:58.750 --> 24:59.550
doing my part.

25:01.310 --> 25:03.420
I just have a little hobby

25:04.160 --> 25:06.350
I haven't quit yet.

25:10.030 --> 25:11.830
I'll turn into a dog if I lie to you.

25:11.830 --> 25:12.560
Come with me.

25:15.510 --> 25:16.400
Let's go.

25:24.000 --> 25:24.660
Have a seat.

25:24.960 --> 25:26.510
I want to ask you about someone.

25:26.510 --> 25:27.030
Who?

25:27.830 --> 25:29.030
I don't know his name.

25:29.270 --> 25:31.130
He looks like a young cultivator.

25:31.480 --> 25:32.480
He has black hair,

25:32.640 --> 25:34.440
a red mole between his eyebrows,

25:34.840 --> 25:36.880
doesn't dress like someone
from the Central Plains,

25:36.880 --> 25:38.170
and has good cultivation techniques.

25:38.170 --> 25:38.910
Lately,

25:39.030 --> 25:40.830
he should be at the Void Stage.

25:56.000 --> 25:56.960
Absolutely not.

25:58.060 --> 26:00.110
I just suddenly remembered that

26:00.880 --> 26:02.810
I have to confess something to you.

26:03.750 --> 26:04.400
What is it?

26:05.880 --> 26:07.050
Two years ago,

26:07.400 --> 26:09.430
before I got addicted to gambling,

26:09.640 --> 26:10.880
I had a lover

26:11.720 --> 26:12.840
in the brothel.

26:15.310 --> 26:16.400
What a coincidence.

26:16.400 --> 26:17.680
The person you are looking for

26:17.680 --> 26:19.270
is related to my lover.

26:26.590 --> 26:27.390
Two years ago,

26:27.560 --> 26:28.640
someone gave my lover

26:28.640 --> 26:29.370
a sum of money

26:29.480 --> 26:30.740
to have a child for him.

26:31.400 --> 26:31.920
Then,

26:32.170 --> 26:33.590
she left with him for less than 2 months

26:33.590 --> 26:34.920
and came back pregnant.

26:35.030 --> 26:36.000
When she came back,

26:36.000 --> 26:37.400
she kept muttering to me,

26:37.440 --> 26:38.970
saying she got a great deal.

26:39.160 --> 26:41.720
She said the one who asked for help
was a cultivator.

26:41.720 --> 26:43.110
He was a handsome young man,

26:43.110 --> 26:43.930
generous

26:43.960 --> 26:44.960
and gentle to her.

26:45.160 --> 26:46.160
She stayed at his house for 2 months.

26:46.160 --> 26:47.560
It was wonderful for her.

26:48.400 --> 26:49.640
Back then, she told me that

26:49.640 --> 26:50.700
the cultivator had

26:50.970 --> 26:53.100
a cinnabar mole between his eyebrows.

26:53.880 --> 26:54.590
Where is

26:55.070 --> 26:56.070
this lady now?

26:57.200 --> 26:58.200
She died long ago.

26:58.310 --> 27:00.310
Bled to death giving birth.

27:00.640 --> 27:01.840
What about the child?

27:02.710 --> 27:04.710
I saw her a few times before she left.

27:04.730 --> 27:05.260
Her belly

27:05.790 --> 27:06.750
was huge.

27:07.640 --> 27:09.140
She said she was carrying a boy.

27:09.140 --> 27:10.530
I was very curious then.

27:11.070 --> 27:12.640
How did she know it was a boy

27:13.000 --> 27:14.480
before the child was even born?

27:14.480 --> 27:16.080
Anyway, she was in bad shape.

27:16.350 --> 27:17.440
She was thin and weak.

27:17.440 --> 27:18.300
She passed away

27:18.350 --> 27:19.810
right after giving birth.

27:20.160 --> 27:21.260
And strangely enough,

27:21.260 --> 27:22.480
when the child was born,

27:22.480 --> 27:23.540
it really was a boy.

27:24.480 --> 27:25.830
Where is the child?

27:26.440 --> 27:27.750
I don't know about that.

27:27.750 --> 27:30.080
He was taken away
by the man you mentioned.

27:30.270 --> 27:31.930
But I just thought of someone.

27:32.200 --> 27:33.200
Maybe she'd know.

27:36.240 --> 27:38.570
Do you know the best dancer
in North Xiang,

27:38.830 --> 27:39.640
Yaoniang?

27:41.400 --> 27:42.000
Yaoniang?

27:42.650 --> 27:43.610
Don't get me wrong.

27:43.610 --> 27:44.510
My lover used to be

27:44.510 --> 27:45.830
friends with Yaoniang.

27:45.830 --> 27:47.120
They were close to each other.

27:47.120 --> 27:47.850
Go ask her.

27:48.030 --> 27:50.030
She definitely knows more than I do.

27:51.720 --> 27:52.450
Where is she?

27:53.240 --> 27:54.570
Tianxiang Restaurant.

27:58.990 --> 28:00.170
[Tianxiang Restaurant]

28:12.830 --> 28:13.420
Excuse me.

28:13.420 --> 28:14.830
Call the manager here.

28:15.170 --> 28:16.430
I have some questions.

28:20.670 --> 28:21.400
Sir,

28:21.720 --> 28:23.180
are you here for Yaoniang?

28:25.070 --> 28:26.200
You are smart, Miss.

28:29.720 --> 28:30.550
Then I can't help you

28:30.550 --> 28:31.550
with this favor.

28:32.270 --> 28:32.920
Look.

28:33.580 --> 28:35.440
All the gentlemen in this building

28:35.440 --> 28:36.880
are here for Yaoniang.

28:37.400 --> 28:38.880
Everyone is offering money

28:38.880 --> 28:40.340
to see her ahead of others.

28:41.060 --> 28:42.340
But Yaoniang can't receive

28:42.340 --> 28:43.200
so many people.

28:43.570 --> 28:44.830
Please wait a little longer.

28:44.830 --> 28:45.830
If you feel bored,

28:46.120 --> 28:47.110
you can find other girls

28:47.110 --> 28:48.370
to drink wine with you.

28:56.070 --> 28:57.860
I just want to ask a few questions.

28:57.860 --> 28:59.260
How long do I have to wait?

28:59.680 --> 29:00.750
Looking at this situation,

29:00.750 --> 29:02.160
you'd be lucky to see her by the

29:02.160 --> 29:03.270
first watch, and speak to her

29:03.270 --> 29:04.030
by the third.

29:10.680 --> 29:11.240
Friend,

29:11.610 --> 29:14.340
is this your first time
at Tianxiang Restaurant?

29:14.830 --> 29:16.030
Please enlighten me.

29:17.110 --> 29:18.720
Yaoniang is Tianxiang Restaurant's

29:18.720 --> 29:19.960
most famous dancer.

29:20.240 --> 29:22.880
Her Huxuan dance
is famous all over North Xiang.

29:22.880 --> 29:24.270
Although she is from a brothel,

29:24.270 --> 29:25.610
she is pure

29:25.640 --> 29:27.040
and never sells her body.

29:27.270 --> 29:28.130
Half a year ago,

29:28.640 --> 29:30.680
Lord Qian, the magistrate of Phoenix City,

29:30.680 --> 29:31.740
took a fancy to her.

29:32.200 --> 29:33.030
Lord Qian

29:33.550 --> 29:34.960
is already 60 years old.

29:35.750 --> 29:38.240
He has a fierce wife at home,

29:38.440 --> 29:41.100
but still wants to take
Yaoniang as a concubine.

29:42.880 --> 29:43.880
He's using his power to oppress people,

29:43.880 --> 29:44.960
forcibly take a civilian lady,

29:44.960 --> 29:46.350
all to make her a concubine.

29:46.350 --> 29:47.510
How shameless.

29:47.930 --> 29:49.530
But Yaoniang didn't want to.

29:49.880 --> 29:51.790
She said she already had a sweetheart

29:51.790 --> 29:53.830
and would marry him soon.

29:54.190 --> 29:55.120
Lord Qian

29:55.310 --> 29:56.710
didn't want to force her.

29:57.030 --> 29:58.630
He gave Yaoniang half a year.

29:58.640 --> 30:00.100
If she really got married,

30:00.440 --> 30:01.510
he'd let it be.

30:01.790 --> 30:02.880
If not,

30:03.510 --> 30:05.240
she'd have to be his concubine.

30:06.110 --> 30:07.590
Now the 6 months are up,

30:08.160 --> 30:10.090
but Yaoniang is still not married.

30:11.110 --> 30:11.920
We thought

30:12.550 --> 30:14.680
Lord Qian would take her as a concubine

30:14.750 --> 30:15.750
for sure.

30:16.270 --> 30:17.160
Unexpectedly,

30:17.550 --> 30:20.110
Tianxiang Restaurant suddenly announced

30:20.510 --> 30:22.880
a flower-viewing event.

30:23.400 --> 30:24.240
Yaoniang

30:24.880 --> 30:27.400
will be retiring with her new
Luanxue Dance at the event.

30:27.400 --> 30:27.960
See,

30:28.720 --> 30:30.960
the wealthy flower-viewers in the city

30:31.240 --> 30:32.440
are all gathered here

30:32.510 --> 30:33.650
just to catch a glimpse

30:33.650 --> 30:35.540
of the top dancer in North Xiang.

30:39.510 --> 30:40.160
Friend.

30:40.830 --> 30:42.290
If you also like Yaoniang,

30:42.750 --> 30:43.880
you can also make an offer

30:43.880 --> 30:45.110
and join the bidding.

30:46.070 --> 30:47.670
As long as your offer is high,

30:47.720 --> 30:49.380
you will have a chance tonight

30:49.830 --> 30:52.310
to have a good chat with her all night.

31:10.720 --> 31:11.780
Thank you, friend.

31:25.160 --> 31:26.960
Isn't that the boy from Lingji Mountain?

31:26.960 --> 31:27.960
Why is he here too?

31:28.750 --> 31:29.880
What a coincidence.

31:37.200 --> 31:38.260
Keep an eye on her.

31:38.680 --> 31:40.280
Today is Yaoniang's big day.

31:40.410 --> 31:41.600
Don't let her run away or get lost

31:41.600 --> 31:42.660
and cause trouble.

31:43.200 --> 31:44.130
After today,

31:44.160 --> 31:45.830
we can take our time disciplining her.

31:45.830 --> 31:46.630
Rest assured.

31:47.440 --> 31:48.480
If you do well,

31:48.770 --> 31:50.010
you will be rewarded.

32:16.680 --> 32:17.680
Where is my sword?

32:18.240 --> 32:19.540
It's so lively outside,

32:19.540 --> 32:21.400
but we have to guard the door here.

32:21.440 --> 32:23.030
I also want to see Yaoniang's dance.

32:23.030 --> 32:23.690
Enough.

32:23.850 --> 32:24.640
Making you guard here

32:24.640 --> 32:25.640
is not a bad thing.

32:25.680 --> 32:26.720
The young lady inside

32:26.720 --> 32:27.780
has a great figure.

32:27.960 --> 32:28.750
I'm telling you,

32:28.750 --> 32:30.010
Madam Wu values her very much.

32:30.010 --> 32:31.160
She wants to make her
the new top courtesan

32:31.160 --> 32:32.490
after Yaoniang leaves.

32:36.960 --> 32:37.480
You...

32:37.720 --> 32:39.200
Shut up if you don't want to die.

32:39.200 --> 32:40.200
I have a question.

32:40.270 --> 32:42.400
Answer well, and I'll spare your life.

32:44.440 --> 32:46.700
I said I just wanted to
ask you a question.

33:02.310 --> 33:03.710
What are you waiting for?

33:03.830 --> 33:04.650
Are we still

33:04.830 --> 33:06.090
looking for Yaoniang?

33:13.160 --> 33:14.490
What's the matter, Sir?

33:15.210 --> 33:16.590
When Yaoniang appears later,

33:16.590 --> 33:17.550
how should I bid?

33:18.400 --> 33:19.750
Peonies are 50 taels each.

33:19.750 --> 33:20.810
Roses are 20 taels.

33:20.920 --> 33:22.920
The rest are 10 taels each.

33:23.590 --> 33:25.350
Sir, you can exchange money for flowers.

33:25.350 --> 33:26.960
When the ladies appear later,

33:26.960 --> 33:28.030
if you see someone you like,

33:28.030 --> 33:28.920
you can put the flowers

33:28.920 --> 33:30.270
in the basket in front.

33:31.070 --> 33:32.330
The type and number of flowers

33:32.330 --> 33:33.650
represent the bid.

33:34.110 --> 33:35.450
Today, besides Yaoniang,

33:35.450 --> 33:37.380
there are other ladies dancing too.

33:37.380 --> 33:39.290
Sir, you have many choices.

33:42.790 --> 33:43.440
Here.

33:45.450 --> 33:47.840
100 taels is indeed a lot,

33:48.100 --> 33:49.360
but for this occasion,

33:49.450 --> 33:51.160
I'm afraid it won't win the bid.

33:51.160 --> 33:53.220
If you don't want to join the fun, Sir,

33:53.400 --> 33:55.660
100 taels is enough to find someone else.

33:56.200 --> 33:57.110
For example,

33:57.960 --> 33:58.680
me.

33:59.390 --> 34:00.970
I'd be very happy to dance for you,

34:00.970 --> 34:01.830
even for free.

34:01.830 --> 34:02.680
Here.

34:05.680 --> 34:06.540
Thank you, Sir.

34:09.840 --> 34:10.400
I say,

34:11.150 --> 34:12.330
if Su Taiyi knew

34:12.350 --> 34:13.480
the money he left you

34:13.500 --> 34:14.630
was spent like this,

34:14.980 --> 34:15.679
he'd be

34:15.710 --> 34:16.909
rolling in his grave.

34:21.590 --> 34:22.190
Yaoniang.

34:22.530 --> 34:23.790
Why are you still here?

34:23.949 --> 34:24.889
The event is about to start.

34:24.889 --> 34:25.920
Go and prepare.

34:36.510 --> 34:37.110
Yaoniang,

34:37.320 --> 34:38.050
listen to me.

34:38.670 --> 34:39.800
So you finally came.

34:40.400 --> 34:41.440
I thought you were scared

34:41.440 --> 34:42.969
of that old man's authority

34:43.120 --> 34:44.650
and didn't dare come for me.

34:45.280 --> 34:45.800
Yes.

34:46.260 --> 34:47.659
I really was scared then.

34:47.960 --> 34:49.230
But I'm not scared anymore.

34:49.230 --> 34:50.150
I'll take you away.

34:50.150 --> 34:51.150
We'll leave North Xiang,

34:51.150 --> 34:51.670
flee far away,

34:51.670 --> 34:52.800
and never come back.

34:57.670 --> 34:58.930
I didn't see anything.

35:00.630 --> 35:01.230
Thank you.

35:01.360 --> 35:02.000
Let's go.

35:14.280 --> 35:15.070
It's starting.

35:15.070 --> 35:16.870
Yuniang, please go on the stage.

35:36.590 --> 35:37.850
Which one is Yaoniang?

35:38.880 --> 35:39.740
You don't know?

35:40.230 --> 35:42.030
Naturally, I don't know either.

35:50.320 --> 35:51.360
Better to reward the wrong one

35:51.360 --> 35:52.230
than miss the right one.

35:52.230 --> 35:52.910
How about

35:53.440 --> 35:54.500
we hang it up first?

36:22.180 --> 36:26.700
Nice!

36:27.000 --> 36:28.590
Nice!

36:29.710 --> 36:30.880
Nice!

36:31.110 --> 36:33.150
Nice!

36:33.250 --> 36:33.840
So nice.

36:33.840 --> 36:35.000
So nice.

36:47.670 --> 36:48.730
Such a great dance.

36:49.400 --> 36:51.400
Nice!

36:51.840 --> 36:52.630
So nice.

36:53.630 --> 36:54.700
Absolutely wonderful.

36:54.700 --> 36:56.090
Nice!

36:57.070 --> 36:58.400
This one looks like her.

36:59.150 --> 36:59.840
This one?

37:12.030 --> 37:14.400
Second floor, Chuan Room—Mr. Lu

37:14.540 --> 37:15.890
has bid 500 taels

37:16.270 --> 37:18.640
for a private meeting with Yuniang

37:19.360 --> 37:20.820
to enjoy a graceful dance

37:20.840 --> 37:22.840
beneath the flowers and moonlight!

37:24.110 --> 37:26.510
Nice!

37:28.670 --> 37:29.590
Yuniang?

37:30.480 --> 37:32.150
This isn't Yaoniang.

37:33.150 --> 37:34.150
What should we do?

37:35.590 --> 37:36.650
What else can we do?

37:37.110 --> 37:38.370
Keep hanging rewards.

37:48.370 --> 37:49.300
Why are you here?

37:50.400 --> 37:51.200
Do you know me?

37:54.710 --> 37:56.310
Why do you look so familiar?

37:59.630 --> 38:00.230
Forget it.

38:00.670 --> 38:01.870
That doesn't matter.

38:02.480 --> 38:03.480
Do you drink wine?

38:17.520 --> 38:18.590
Come, let's drink.

38:18.710 --> 38:19.280
Come on.

38:19.840 --> 38:20.440
Come on.

38:20.800 --> 38:21.510
Drink up.

38:22.190 --> 38:23.090
This trip is totally worth it.

38:23.090 --> 38:23.840
Yeah.

38:23.920 --> 38:24.590
Eat, eat.

38:24.740 --> 38:26.260
Tonight is really worth it.

38:26.260 --> 38:26.780
Nice!

38:27.480 --> 38:28.230
Decisive.

38:28.510 --> 38:29.230
What a beautiful figure.

38:29.230 --> 38:29.960
Cheers.

38:55.070 --> 38:55.690
Yaoniang.

38:55.790 --> 38:57.280
Why are you here drinking?

38:57.560 --> 38:58.390
Come with me, quick.

38:58.390 --> 38:59.650
You are going on stage.

39:06.960 --> 39:07.590
Come on.

39:08.000 --> 39:08.860
Keep drinking.

39:11.980 --> 39:14.310
Where's the lady who was drinking with me?

39:15.480 --> 39:16.190
Sir,

39:16.800 --> 39:18.000
do you want more wine?

39:18.400 --> 39:18.960
No need.

39:20.920 --> 39:22.080
Sir, you act as if

39:22.110 --> 39:24.190
you've never held a lady's hand before.

39:24.190 --> 39:25.290
Why so shy?

39:26.070 --> 39:26.590
Friend.

39:27.210 --> 39:29.210
If you waste your luck with the lady,

39:29.220 --> 39:30.850
you'll be cursed by heaven.

39:36.710 --> 39:37.230
Friend,

39:37.920 --> 39:39.720
your target, Yaoniang, is here.

39:40.710 --> 39:42.440
Why didn't you tell us earlier?

39:42.960 --> 39:43.800
Everyone here

39:44.140 --> 39:45.500
is after Yaoniang.

39:46.100 --> 39:47.560
You guys are rich and powerful.

39:47.560 --> 39:48.960
I can't compete with you.

39:49.110 --> 39:50.040
So I might as well

39:50.110 --> 39:51.770
let you bid on a few more ladies

39:52.000 --> 39:53.330
and deplete your money.

39:53.880 --> 39:54.590
Friend,

39:55.150 --> 39:57.190
you're using the
Thirty-Six Stratagems here?

39:57.190 --> 39:58.450
That's playing dirty.

40:21.030 --> 40:21.670
Yaoniang,

40:21.970 --> 40:22.960
why aren't you dancing?

40:22.960 --> 40:24.110
Yeah, why not?

40:24.590 --> 40:26.960
Dance, dance, Yaoniang!

40:28.190 --> 40:29.230
Dance!

40:30.000 --> 40:30.760
Dance!

40:32.080 --> 40:32.680
Sir.

40:34.190 --> 40:34.920
No, thanks.

40:36.840 --> 40:37.900
Hurry up and dance!

40:38.340 --> 40:39.270
Hurry up!
